headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Smuggler Sell Missions
content: It’s dangerous to let contraband sit dormant in your Warehouses, but it’s also financially irresponsible, especially when Smuggler Sell Missions are paying back 2X GTA$ & RP this week. Load up and move your stock across the map, but stay frosty, lest marauders try to intercept your delivery.
